profile:
The Country Roofer Inc. is owned and operated by Justan Lavigne. Born and raised in the Fredericton area, Justin is aware of the needs of the local people and uses his knowledge to offer premium roofing solutions in Nackawic, Harvey, Oromocto and all surrounding areas. With over 26 years of experience in the roofing industry, we are capable of meeting all your roofing requirements, be it installation or repair. We specialize in metal and asphalt roofing and are fully insured to provide services that you can trust.


As your go-to roofers, we offer certified services, 7 years of workmanship warranty, competitive rates, and free estimates on all our services. If you wish to request a free quote on the service you require, reach out to us.
